title: Apple iPhone XS Max
description: Apple iPhone XS Max is the most pricey iPhone release of 2018 and one of the most expensive smartphones available in the current market. But it is also one of the most advanced smartphones of today considering its features and performance.The 6.5-inch huge super retina custom OLED display should give you the most pleasant experience of viewing an smartphone display. The color accuracy is pretty impressive. iPhone X had the best camera in a smartphone last year according to most of the major smartphone portals. It gets even better in XS Max. The low light noise is significantly reduced through larger and deeper pixels and color accuracy has also been well-improved. Stunning 4K video recording is available as usual. The battery backup and technology is sound and reliable. Performance is smooth, the body is made of high-quality natural robust material and it has precise, elegant finishing with water and dust-proof feature.

title: iPhone X
description: Some say (including Apple of course) that the new iPhone X is the smartphone of the future. This can be highly arguable since Samsung is thinking about out of the box folding display technology and some companies are working on improved modular phone concept like the Google Ara. This discussion can go on for hours. So, for now, let’s concentrate on the new iPhone X. What is new, what are the specialities?The first thing one notices is the somewhat weird display. The display design on top together with the camera setup is weird. I won’t buy any other comment on that. But on the other hand, all buttons and bezels disappearing completely from the front is surely something amazing and futuristic. The previous aluminum frame has been replaced with stainless steel which makes it more elegant and valuable piece of art. The display is now 5.8 inches big. But because of its design, the phone itself is not as big as a regular 5.8-inch phone. Which is purely smart. Apple has finally moved from IPS LCD technology to super AMOLED which Samsung has been using successfully for years. If you do not understand the difference, Super AMOLED retina display is more awesome than any other display out there in 2017.
